snippet.title: Destiny 2 Expansion II: Warmind Prologue Cinematic
snippet.description:
Ana Bray, a Guardian long thought lost, searches for a connection to her past…one that could be buried forever beneath the polar ice of Mars. 

Expansion II: Warmind arrives May 8. Purchase the Destiny 2 Expansion Pass and get access to both Expansion I and Expansion II. https://www.destinythegame.com/buy 

For development updates, follow Bungie on Twitter and Instagram:

https://www.twitter.com/bungie 
https://www.instagram.com/bungie/

For Destiny 2 news, follow Destiny on Twitter and Instagram: 

https://www.twitter.com/destinythegame 
https://www.instagram.com/destinythegame
